<html>

<head>
  <style media="screen">
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:700|Source+Sans+Pro');

    body {
      background-color: #2146ff;
      background: url("https://www.toptal.com/designers/subtlepatterns/patterns/struckaxiom.png");
    }

    label {
      font-weight: 600;
    }


    .form-control:focus {
      border-color: black;
      box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px black;
    }

    .btn-lg:focus {
      outline: none;
      box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px black;
    }

    .emailButton:focus {
      border-color: black;
      box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px black;
    }

    .searchBox {
      background-color: white;
      min-height: 200px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border-style: solid;
      border-width: 2px;
      margin: 5%;
    }

    h1 {
      color: white;
      font-size: 4em;
      color: black;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: #ffaf00;
      /* Will override color (regardless of order) */
      -webkit-text-stroke-width: .03em;
      -webkit-text-stroke-color: black;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    h3 {
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: black;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: #581845;
      /* Will override color (regardless of order) */
      -webkit-text-stroke-width: .05em;
      -webkit-text-stroke-color: black;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .form > p {
      font-size: 0.8em;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", sans-serif;
    }

    .emailButton {
      font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", sans-serif;
      color: black;
      border-style: solid;
      border-width: 1px;
      border-color: black;
      margin-left: 5px;
      background-color: white;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .emailButton:hover,
    .emailButton:active {
      background-color: #2146ff;
      color: white;
      transition-duration: .3s;
    }

    .emailButton:not( :hover) {
      transition-duration: .3s;
    }

    .search {
      margin: 5% 10%;
    }

    .form-group {
      font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
    }


    .form-control {
      border-color: lightgrey;
      border-radius: 5px !important;
    }

    .form-control:not( :hover),
    .form-control:not( :active) {
      transition-duration: .3s;
    }

    .form-control:hover,
    .form-control:active {
      border-color: black !important;
      border-radius: 5px !important;
      transition-duration: .3s;
    }

    .errorMessage {
      display: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2"></div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 searchBox">

        <div class="form search">
          <h1>Hello there, <br> you requested a password change <br><a href="<%=link%>">Click here</a><br>to reset your password</h1>
          <h3>With love, from <img src="https://marketing-image-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/fd101f8e53b0fd0718118a98b6d109f76509da8007e528d4d86c41f946f49e524115cdfe40c1a3c92c730fb08239347994b6e9bef05d4cf7382f120d5af8bf8b.png" width="30"></img>&nbsp;Musicoin<br><a href="mailto:support@musicoin.org">support@musicoin.org</a></h3>
          <p>If you did not request this password reset, please ignore this email</p>
          <p>We never send you unsolicited emails asking for password resets and similar. Stay safe and stay sharp.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
